@startuml Context Map

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

title Context Map - Logistica de Ultima Milla

rectangle "<<Bounded Context>>\nPedidos\n(Core)" as Pedidos #LightBlue
rectangle "<<Bounded Context>>\nRepartidores\n(Core)" as Repartidores #LightGreen
rectangle "<<Bounded Context>>\nDespacho\n(Core)" as Despacho #LightYellow
rectangle "<<Bounded Context>>\nRutas\n(Supporting)" as Rutas #LightCoral
rectangle "<<Bounded Context>>\nTracking\n(Supporting)" as Tracking #Lavender
rectangle "<<Bounded Context>>\nIncidencias\n(Generic)" as Incidencias #MistyRose

rectangle "<<External>>\nSistema de\nNotificaciones" as Notif #LightGray
rectangle "<<External>>\nPlataformas\nE-commerce" as Ecomm #LightGray
rectangle "<<External>>\nPartners\nExternos" as Partners #LightGray

' Relaciones entre BCs
Pedidos -down-> Despacho : <<Customer/Supplier>>\nPedidos provee datos\nal despacho
Repartidores -down-> Despacho : <<Customer/Supplier>>\nRepartidores provee\ndisponibilidad
Despacho -right-> Rutas : <<Customer/Supplier>>\nDespacho alimenta\nrutas
Pedidos -right-> Tracking : <<Conformist>>\nTracking se adapta\nal modelo de Pedidos
Pedidos -left-> Incidencias : <<Customer/Supplier>>\nIncidencias referencia\npedidos

' ACL con sistemas externos
Tracking -down-> Notif : <<ACL>>\nAnti-Corruption Layer
Pedidos -up-> Ecomm : <<ACL>>\nAdapter pattern
Pedidos -up-> Partners : <<ACL>>\nAdapter pattern

' Shared Kernel
note bottom of Pedidos
    Shared Kernel: Direccion,
    ContactInfo, DomainEvent, EventBus
end note

@enduml
